a:2:{i:0;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:3:"196";s:5:"title";s:36:"Tự làm quả cầu hoa rực rỡ";s:3:"url";s:47:"/meo-hay/chi-tiet-196/tu-lam-qua-cau-hoa-ruc-ro";s:4:"desc";s:145:"Chỉ với vài bông hoa lan cùng quả cầu xốp hí hoáy trong vài phút là chúng mình có ngay một quả cầu hoa tuyệt đẹp.";s:5:"image";a:2:{i:420;s:43:"http://meonho.net/upload/meohay/196/420.jpg";i:157;s:43:"http://meonho.net/upload/meohay/196/157.jpg";}s:4:"step";a:0:{}s:7:"content";s:4140:"<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Nguy&ecirc;n liệu :</em><br /></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">- Quả cầu xốp<br />- Hoa lan tường<br />- K&eacute;o hoặc k&igrave;m cắt hoa<br />- Ruy băng<br />- Ghim</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-B6BXH5FtrS0%2FU0wiZ2AlTsI%2FAAAAAAAAEPU%2FHsdeTW9zT10%2Fs1600%2F1.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-B6BXH5FtrS0/U0wiZ2AlTsI/AAAAAAAAEPU/HsdeTW9zT10/s1600/1.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>C&aacute;ch l&agrave;m :</strong></em></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Bước 1:</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-J1tZm7J2a04%2FU0wiaELjbmI%2FAAAAAAAAEPY%2FSs-aE9wP8XU%2Fs1600%2F2.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-J1tZm7J2a04/U0wiaELjbmI/AAAAAAAAEPY/Ss-aE9wP8XU/s1600/2.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Đầu ti&ecirc;n, c&aacute;c ấy cắt rời từng đầu b&ocirc;ng hoa d&agrave;i khoảng 7-8 cm (Bao gồm cả th&acirc;n c&agrave;nh v&agrave; b&ocirc;ng hoa).</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Bước 2:</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Dk4bMaQytkg%2FU0wiZ4vzSDI%2FAAAAAAAAEPc%2FlTNOchNNuDQ%2Fs1600%2F3.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Dk4bMaQytkg/U0wiZ4vzSDI/AAAAAAAAEPc/lTNOchNNuDQ/s1600/3.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Sau đ&oacute;, bạn cắm thẳng từng b&ocirc;ng hoa s&aacute;t nhau, phủ k&iacute;n bề mặt xốp.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Bước 3:</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-TqAq24fuMFM%2FU0wibAzP0HI%2FAAAAAAAAEPs%2FpKBagAwmBp0%2Fs1600%2F4.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-TqAq24fuMFM/U0wibAzP0HI/AAAAAAAAEPs/pKBagAwmBp0/s1600/4.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">C&aacute;c ấy cắt một đoạn ruy băng, gập đ&ocirc;i lại với chiều d&agrave;i mong muốn rồi ghim v&agrave;o trong th&acirc;n xốp bằng kim ghim n&agrave;y.</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-CDAD4KVZfqk%2FU0wibYnt1gI%2FAAAAAAAAEPw%2FdknnG6T6Ks0%2Fs1600%2F6.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-CDAD4KVZfqk/U0wibYnt1gI/AAAAAAAAEPw/dknnG6T6Ks0/s1600/6.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Đơn giản vậy thui l&agrave; bạn đ&atilde; c&oacute; quả cầu hoa xinh xắn n&agrave;y rồi.</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-_to7QiHAWBI%2FU0wibey5jVI%2FAAAAAAAAEP8%2FOhahMyhSZEA%2Fs1600%2F7.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-_to7QiHAWBI/U0wibey5jVI/AAAAAAAAEP8/OhahMyhSZEA/s1600/7.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Nh&igrave;n những đ&oacute;a hoa nở phủ k&iacute;n m&agrave; đ&atilde; mắt gh&ecirc;, cứ ngắm ho&agrave;i &agrave;.</p>";s:7:"created";s:8:"15/04/14";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:3:"tip";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:8:"HANDMADE";s:10:"type_label";s:11:"Thủ công";}i:1;N;}